data.description: Looking for your dream home in the beautiful city of Cape Coral, Florida? Your search ends here! Don't miss out on this incredible opportunity to own the lowest priced pool home in the area.This fantastic starter pool home is perfect for those who appreciate the Florida lifestyle. Imagine spending your weekends by the pool or hosting memorable gatherings on your spacious screened-in lanai. Your family and friends will love the large, fenced backyard for outdoor activities.Located in a serene and desirable neighborhood that's NOT in a flood zone, you can have peace of mind during all seasons. With 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms, the split floor plan offers the privacy and convenience you desire.The owner has already initiated some renovation work on the property, allowing you to add your personal touch and transform this house into your dream home. Call today for your private showing!
